### Artist Management API Tests

### 1. Registrazione Artista
POST http://localhost:3000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rhaonthemoon@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Raffaele Pastura",
  "artistName": "Rha"
}

### 2. Login Artista
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rhaonthemoon@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 3. Crea Show (Bozza)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/shows
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Concerto Rock 2025",
  "description": "Serata rock incredibile con band emergenti",
  "date": "2025-12-31T20:00:00Z",
  "venue": "Teatro Grande Milano",
  "status": "draft"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("show_id", response.body._id);
%}

### 4. Lista Show dell'Artista
GET http://localhost:3000/api/shows
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. Aggiorna Show
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/shows/{{show_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Concerto Rock 2025 - AGGIORNATO",
  "description": "Serata rock con ospiti speciali!",
  "status": "pending"
}

### 6. Elimina Show
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/shows/69090dcf99e9162cf205da8c
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

