### 7. Registrazione Admin (temporaneo - da rimuovere in produzione)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "name": "Admin User",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 8. Login Admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 9. Admin - Lista Show in Attesa
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/shows/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 10. Admin - Approva Show
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/shows/{{show_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "approved",
  "adminNotes": "Show approvato! Ottima proposta."
}

### 11. Admin - Rifiuta Show
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/shows/{{show_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "rejected",
  "adminNotes": "Mancano informazioni sul venue"
}

